Môn: TIẾNG ANH
1. Tom’s brother is _______.
A. slim
B. fat
C. short
D. tall
Đáp án: D. tall

2. Tom’s brother is wearing _______.
A. glasses
B. a blue T-shirt
C. a green T-shirt
D. green shorts
Đáp án: B. a blue T-shirt

3. Jenny’s sister has _______.
A. short hair
B. black hair
C. brown hair
D. long hair
Đáp án: D. long hair

4. Jenny’s sister is kind and _______.
A. friendly
B. helpful
C. funny
D. lazy
Đáp án: B. helpful

5. Tom has one _______.
A. sister
B. brother
C. friend
D. uncle
Đáp án: A. sister

6. Tom’s brother is _______ and really friendly.
A. funny
B. lazy
C. kind
D. mean
Đáp án: A. funny

7. Jenny’s sister is _______ years old.
A. 18
B. 26
C. 16
D. 8
Đáp án: B. 26

8. Jenny’s sister is _______.
A. fat
B. short
C. tall
D. slim
Đáp án: C. tall

9. Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. puppets
B. shows
C. orders
D. stands
Đáp án: A. puppets

10. Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. fixes
B. pushes
C. misses
D. goes
Đáp án: D. goes

11. Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. fireworks
B. flowers
C. gifts
D. shops
Đáp án: B. flowers

12. Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. history
B. biology
C. village
D. literature
Đáp án: B. biology

13. Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. indoor
B. festival
C. like
D. dinner
Đáp án: C. like

14. Which word has the underlined part pronounced differently from that of the others?
A. light
B. stripe
C. slim
D. fine
Đáp án: C. slim

15. Which word has a different stress pattern from that of the others?
A. secret
B. scary
C. event
D. outdoor
Đáp án: C. event

16. Which word has a different stress pattern from that of the others?
A. balcony
B. subject
C. adventure
D. favorite
Đáp án: C. adventure

17. Which word has a different stress pattern from that of the others?
A. selfish
B. picnic
C. hotel
D. homework
Đáp án: C. hotel

18. We like English, physics _______ biology.
A. to
B. or
C. and
D. so
Đáp án: C. and

19. We love playing soccer _______ badminton in our free time.
A. and
B. or
C. on
D. with
Đáp án: A. and

20. There isn’t a gym _______ a swimming pool near my house.
A. and
B. or
C. but
D. for
Đáp án: B. or

21. She doesn’t like math _______ biology.
A. and
B. or
C. but
D. for
Đáp án: B. or

22. His hometown is in the south _______ Italy.
A. in
B. on
C. at
D. of
Đáp án: D. of

23. Cần Thơ is in the Mekong Delta, _______ the Hậu River.
A. for
B. in
C. on
D. at
Đáp án: C. on

24. The restaurant opens _______ Sundays.
A. of
B. for
C. at
D. on
Đáp án: D. on

25. Students don’t go to school _______ Sundays.
A. in
B. at
C. on
D. of
Đáp án: C. on

26. Tom has Biology, Geography _______ Friday.
A. at
B. on
C. in
D. with
Đáp án: B. on

27. Our Math lesson usually finishes _______ 4.00 p.m.
A. on
B. of
C. at
D. for
Đáp án: C. at

28. My brother sometimes plays game "Free Fire" with his friends _______ the evening.
A. on
B. for
C. at
D. in
Đáp án: D. in

29. What do you do _______ your free time?
A. on
B. in
C. at
D. to
Đáp án: B. in

30. My best friend is very kind ……… lazy.
A. but
B. and
C. so
D. or
Đáp án: A. but

31. Excuse me, what size are ……… pants over there?
A. this
B. that
C. these
D. those
Đáp án: D. those

32. The new ship has got a ……… with a lot of books.
A. cabin
B. library
C. swimming pool
D. shop
Đáp án: B. library

33. My friends and I _______ camping in the summer. We have a good time.
A. go usually
B. usually go
C. never go
D. go never
Đáp án: B. usually go

34. Nam _______ video games on Sundays.
A. often play
B. plays often
C. often plays
D. play often
Đáp án: C. often plays

35. Nam usually walks to school and he _______ late.
A. never is
B. never go
C. is never
D. are never
Đáp án: C. is never

36. He has _______ and brown eyes.
A. short brown hair
B. brown short hair
C. a short brown hair
D. a brown short hair
Đáp án: A. short brown hair

37. My sister has _______.
A. short black hair
B. short hair black
C. hair short hair
D. black short hair
Đáp án: A. short black hair

38. She has _______.
A. long blond hair
B. blond long hair
C. hair long blond
D. long hair blond
Đáp án: A. long blond hair

39. My sister has _______ hair.
A. black long curly
B. long curly black
C. curly long black
D. long black curly
Đáp án: B. long curly black

40. My favorite subject is math. What’s _______?
A. me
B. my
C. yours
D. her
Đáp án: C. yours

41. What’s your favorite subject? _______ is physics.
A. I
B. My
C. Mine
D. Yours
Đáp án: C. Mine

42. My favorite sport is tennis. What is _______?
A. your
B. yours
C. my
D. mine
Đáp án: B. yours

43. Do you have a ruler? _______ is at home.
A. Their
B. His
C. Ours
D. Mine
Đáp án: D. Mine

44. What’s Peter .........? -> He’s very kind and helpful.
A. do
B. doing
C. love
D. like
Đáp án: D. like

45. Student A: “Where is your hometown?” -> Student B: “………”
A. I love my hometown.
B. It’s in the east of Vietnam.
C. My hometown is a big city.
D. My hometown is very good for growing rice.
Đáp án: B. It’s in the east of Vietnam.

46. My favorite sport is volleyball. What’s ………?
A. their
B. mine
C. yours
D. her
Đáp án: C. yours

47. Anna: What does your best friend look like? -> Lucy: ………
A. She is slim and has long hair.
B. She is so friendly.
C. She likes going shopping.
D. She is eleven years old.
Đáp án: A. She is slim and has long hair.

48. Can I borrow your eraser? I can’t find _______.
A. yours
B. me
C. my
D. mine
Đáp án: D. mine

49. Student A: “What color eyes does your sister have?” – Student B: “_________.”
A. She has blue eyes.
B. She likes green.
C. She has brown hair.
D. She has fair skin.
Đáp án: A. She has blue eyes.

50. Anna: “What does your best friend look like?” – Lucy: “_________.”
A. She is slim and has long hair.
B. She is so friendly.
C. She likes going shopping.
D. She is eleven years old.
Đáp án: A. She is slim and has long hair.

51. Peter: “How often do you go swimming?” -> Jenny: “…………”
A. I go swimming.
B. I sometimes go swimming.
C. I don’t like swimming.
D. I go swimming with my friends.
Đáp án: B. I sometimes go swimming.

52. Student A: “Is he from Italy?” - Student B: “_________”
A. No, he is
B. Yes, he is
C. Yes, he has.
D. No, he hasn’t.
Đáp án: B. Yes, he is

53. Student A: “What kind of book is it?” – Student B: “_________.”
A. It’s a fantasy novel.
B. I like Harry Porter.
C. That’s a good idea.
D. Here you are.
Đáp án: A. It’s a fantasy novel.

54. David: “What are you doing tomorrow?” - Mai: “I’m _______ a barbecue at my house.”
A. going
B. having
C. playing
D. making
Đáp án: B. having

55. Ben: “_______ do people prepare for Christmas?” - Jim: “They decorate their homes.”
A. Why
B. Who
C. How often
D. How
Đáp án: D. How

56. Student A: “Why don’t we have a picnic this weekend?” – Student B: “_________.”
A. Yes, we don’t
B. No, we do
C. Good idea
D. You’re welcome
Đáp án: C. Good idea

57. Student A: “Why don’t you sign up for book club?” – Student B: “_________.”
A. Yes, good idea.
B. I was born in 2003.
C. I live in San Francisco.
D. I clean my bedroom.
Đáp án: A. Yes, good idea.

58. Student A: “Where is your hometown?” – Student B: “_________.”
A. I love my hometown.
B. It’s in the east of Vietnam.
C. My hometown is a big city.
D. My hometown is very good for growing rice.
Đáp án: B. It’s in the east of Vietnam.

59. Student A: “Does your apartment have a gym?” - Student B: “_________.”
A. Yes, it is.
B. No, it isn’t.
C. Yes, it does.
D. No, it does.
Đáp án: C. Yes, it does.

